Version 1.1.0
=============

- you can click on volume slider box in untopped window and new 
  volume will be set.

- added limited support for rewind / forward functions. time isn't 
  updated and also 'big step' (with shift key) is ignored.

- fixed bug when user open Module Info dialog, move to some place on 
  desktop and use slider to scroll down

- fixed bug in random mode playing after playlist reload with another 
  files - random function returned illegal file numbers
